headline.main: Canada Minister Addresses Influx of Asylum-Seekers From US
headline.print_headline: Canada Minister Addresses Influx of Asylum-Seekers From US

lead_paragraph: Canada is enforcing border laws and is willing to put more resources in place to deal with the influx of asylum-seekers from the United States, federal Public Safety Minister Ralph Goodale said Saturday.
